audioContentItems.fileTranscript: Thank you for calling Barnes and Noble. My name is (Your Name). How can I help you?

Hello. My name is Anita Napp. I just called and the nice man told me that he would send me a new copy of my book because it wasn't delivered. As soon as we hung up, my mail was delivered. The book was in today's mail! Can you cancel the new order that was just placed?
No problem, Anita. I would be happy to see if we can cancel the new order for you. Can I have your Order Number, please?
Thank you. Can I please have you verify your email address?
Sure. My email address is anita napp at gmail.com.
Thank you. What is the shipping address on the order?
My address is 1 2 3 Main Street. That's in Anytown, Ohio 4 3 5 5 5.
Thank you. One moment while I research to see if I can cancel the order.

Your order is in a status that I can't make any changes, but I can send a cancel request to the warehouse. I can't promise that it will be cancelled, but we will update you within 24 hours whether we can cancel the order or not. Would you like me to proceed with canceling the order?
Yes, I don't need two copies of the same book.
No problem. One moment while I send the request.

Thank you for your patience. I've sent the request to cancel your order. You'll receive an email within 24 hours to let you know if we can cancel the order or not. You can return it if we can't get it canceled.
You're welcome. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
Thank you for calling Barnes and Noble. Have a great day.

settings.text: This simulation will give you practice in handling advanced call type. You can go through this as many times as desired until you feel confident in the navigation and call flow. The test version of the advanced simulation will provide you with no prompts. You will need to create your own words instead of reading scripting.
Have your audio and microphone ready.
Click into the Order Number field and enter, "6123456789", then press 'Enter.'

settings.expectedValue: Customer requested to cancel the order.
Sent cancel request via OM. Advised will be updated within 24 hours.
